window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>Bus Stop</i> was an immediate commercial and critical success on Broadway in 1955. </p> <p>During a winter storm, a busload of weary travelers are forced to shack up at a roadside diner until morning. Inge was renowned for his in-depth character studies, and <i>Bus Stop</i> is no exception. It offers a warm play about the intersecting lives of eight ordinary people.</p>"; 
